          {
            "title": "If statement",
            "id": 67746,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Como podemos escrever código que se adapta a diferentes situações? Usando a <strong>instrução if</strong>.</p><p>Criamos o código com a palavra-chave <code>if</code> para uma instrução if.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"0\" endIndex=\"2\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>if</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "If statement",
            "id": 67736,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>A instrução if <em>executa o código</em> apenas se o booleano no qual está se baseando for <code>true</code>. É como dizer, <em>se</em> algo é verdadeiro, <em>então</em> faça isso.</p><p><code>\"Hello!\"</code> será exibido no console se definirmos o valor booleano como <code>true</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"false\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "If statement",
            "id": 67734,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Mas e se quisermos <em>pular</em> o código? Usamos <code>false</code> em vez disso.</p><p>Ao definir o valor como <code>false</code>, evitaremos exibir <code>\"Hello!\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"9\" /></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>false</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Conditions",
            "id": 67737,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Valores como <code>true</code> são chamados de <strong>condições</strong>. Declarações que dependem de condições são chamadas de <strong>condicionais</strong>.</p><p>Condições <em>decidem</em> se o código é executado ou ignorado. Elas vêm entre parênteses.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello there&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"4\" endIndex=\"8\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&quot;condition&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello there\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>true</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
