          {
            "title": "Code block ",
            "id": 67738,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>  Declarações <code>if</code> não decidem pular ou executar o <em>código inteiro</em>. Elas apenas tomam decisões sobre um <em>pedaço de código</em>.</p><p>Este trecho de código é chamado de <strong>bloco de código</strong>. Nós o escrevemos entre chaves <code>{}</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I'm a code block!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"10\" endIndex=\"11\" /><option startIndex=\"47\" endIndex=\"48\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"(\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\")\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"I'm a code block!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>{</code> seguido de <code>}</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Expand code block",
            "id": 67741,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Um bloco de código pode ter mais de uma linha. Podemos adicionar quantas linhas quisermos.</p><p>Use <code>console.log()</code> para adicionar mais uma linha no início.</p><code version=\"2\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\" codelang=\"javascript\"><content><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (\" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\") {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Look at me!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;I'm a code block&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"13\" endIndex=\"24\" /><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"38\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"{\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"}\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Look at me!\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"I'm a code block\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>console.log</code> seguido de <code>\"Look at me!\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "True Variable",
            "id": 67744,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Em vez de usar o booleano <code>true</code>, podemos salvá-lo em uma variável e usá-lo como uma condição.</p><p>Crie a variável <code>greet</code> e defina-a como <code>true</code>. Em seguida, use <code>greet</code> como uma condição para a instrução if.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greet = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (greet) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"6\" endIndex=\"11\" /><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"18\" /><option startIndex=\"25\" endIndex=\"30\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"false\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Hello!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>greet</code> seguido de <code>true</code> e finalmente <code>greet</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "False variable",
            "id": 67745,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Usar uma variável definida como <code>false</code> nos permite <em>pular</em> o bloco de código.</p><p>Defina <code>greet</code> como <code>false</code> para evitar imprimir <code>Hello!</code> na saída.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"javascript\" name=\"script.js\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"const\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" greet = \" /><text value=\"false\" class=\"literal\" /><text value=\";\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" (greet) {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"console\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\".log(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Hello!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\");\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"14\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Certifique-se de escolher <code>false</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
